snippet.title: I created a Space Simulator game | Bolt Jam #6 | Gravity Pilot
snippet.description:
You are the last Gravity Pilot! Help the Earth to collect important research by moving on from planet to planet while keeping watch on your fuel.

https://diadas.itch.io/gravity-pilot

Controls

W - Accelerate
D  - Turn right
A - Turn left
Shift - Speed up time
Space - Self-explode
